data.message:
Add Wgs84Sample message type. (#82)

* Add Wgs84Sample message type.

This commit adds a new message type that contains a sensor measurement
in WGS-84 (e.g. GPS sample) and the corresponding sensor location in
relative coordinates (e.g. antenna position).

* Move Wgs84Sample to marti_nav_msgs.

Merge pull request #76 from pjreed/update-route

Add new services to save a route and to update a route's metadata

data.author: P. J. Reed
data.message:
Add new services to save a route and to update a route's metadata

This adds two services:
- SaveRoute
  - Takes a list of route points and saves it
  - If the route's GUID matches an existing route, it will be overwritten
- UpdateRouteMetadata
  - Modifies an existing route
  - Replaces the properties on specified points with new properties

data.message:
Create Route and RoutePoint messages

Route and RoutePoint are very general messages to define a sequence of
achievable poses for a vehicle along with arbitrary metadata about the
route and the point itself.

Requires also creating the dependent KeyValue message.
